            "title": "Cyren to SentinelOne IOC Automation",
            "description": "This playbook fetches IP reputation and/or malware URL threat intelligence indicators from the Cyren CCF API feed and creates corresponding IOC indicators in SentinelOne for automated threat detection and response. Customers can provide one or both Cyren feed tokens.",
            "prerequisites": [
              "1. Cyren CCF JWT Bearer Token for IP Reputation feed (optional if not purchased)",
              "2. Cyren CCF JWT Bearer Token for Malware URL feed (optional if not purchased)",
              "3. At least one of the above tokens is required",
              "4. SentinelOne API Token with Threat Intelligence IOC management permissions",
              "5. SentinelOne Console URL",
              "6. SentinelOne Account ID"
            ],
            "postDeployment": [
              "1. Provide the Cyren_IpReputation_JwtToken if you purchased the IP Reputation feed (leave empty if not).",
              "2. Provide the Cyren_MalwareUrl_JwtToken if you purchased the Malware URL feed (leave empty if not).",
              "3. Configure the SentinelOne_ApiToken, SentinelOne_BaseUrl, and SentinelOne_AccountId parameters.",
              "4. Enable the Logic App and verify the recurrence trigger is set to your desired interval."
            ],
